# Troubleshooting Notes:
# 1. MIME Type Issues: If JS files serve as text/html, check that location blocks are correctly configured
# 2. 404 on Refresh: Ensure try_files directive includes fallback to index.html
# 3. Asset Loading: Verify alias/root path points to directory containing the built files
# 4. Permissions: Ensure nginx user has read access to all files
# 5. Test configuration: nginx -t before reloading 